By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
The sound Om is Brahman. ... You hear the roar of the ocean from a distance. By
following the roar you can reach the ocean. As long as there is the roar,
there must also be the ocean. By following the trail of Om you attain Brahman,
of which the Word is the symbol.
